Phobia pressed a button to activate the CR chamber.

"Try not to get to hurt" Phobia said through his baby, "This ship 
only has one chamber." His ship faced forward, shields on full power 
to the front. "Activate firing sequence 50 percent power, target 
directly in front of the attackers." He didn't want to have to use 
that much power, but he didn't seem to have a choice at this 
particular moment. he'd leave a small crater in front of the 
maximals, hopefully when the dust settled the predacons would be gone.
